# <type>(<scope>): <short summary>

#

# ─── Types ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# feat: New feature

# fix: Bug fix

# docs: Documentation only

# style: Formatting (no code change)

# refactor: Code restructuring (no feat/fix)

# perf: Performance improvement

# test: Adding or updating tests

# build: Build system or external deps

# ci: CI/CD configuration

# chore: Maintenance tasks

# revert: Revert a previous commit

# security: Security fix or hardening

# a11y: Accessibility improvement

# i18n: Internationalization / localization

#

# ─── Scopes (optional) ───────────────────────────────────────────

# sankey, floorplan, adapter, victron, knx, eebus, ocpp, modbus,

# tariff, ai, pwa, store, ui, settings, auth, db, e2e, deps,

# docker, ci, theme

#

# ─── Examples ────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# feat(sankey): add battery charge animation

# fix(ocpp): handle V2X disconnect gracefully

# security(adapter): validate MQTT topic input

# i18n: add missing German translations for tariff page

# perf(store): debounce energy data updates

# a11y(ui): improve screen reader support for sidebar

#

# ─── Rules ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# • Subject: imperative, lowercase, no period, max 100 chars

# • Body: explain _what_ and _why_ (not _how_), wrap at 200

# • Footer: reference issues (Closes #123, Refs #456)

# • Breaking changes: add BREAKING CHANGE: in footer

#
